====导弹快艇====
装备反舰导弹的小型舰只，可以击沉体型庞大的敌舰。最早装备于[[苏联海军|苏联海军]]。
* {{Link-en|OSA-II|Osa-class missile boat}} 205ER 级导弹艇：6艘<ref>{{cite web |url=http://russian-ships.info/eng/warfareboats/project_205.htm |title=Missile boats - Project 205 |publisher=Russian-ships.info |date= |accessdate=2013-06-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110191019/http://russian-ships.info/eng/warfareboats/project_205.htm |archivedate=2013-11-10 }}</ref>

====鱼雷快艇====
装备鱼雷的小型舰只，可以击沉体型庞大的敌舰。最早在[[二战|二战]]中装备于[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]]和[[纳粹德国海军|德意志帝国海军]]。
* “[[大黄蜂|大黄蜂]](''Shershen'')”级鱼雷艇：6艘<ref>{{cite web |url=http://russian-ships.info/eng/warfareboats/project_206.htm |title=Large torpedo boat - Project 206 |publisher=Russian-ships.info |date= |accessdate=2013-06-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512230000/http://russian-ships.info/eng/warfareboats/project_206.htm |archivedate=2014-05-12 }}</ref>

